OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start, with any early
OL,6,Flow cloud soon clearing, leaving
OL,7,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Breezy, with strong
OL,9,Fwinds on coasts. Feeling warm in the
OL,10,Fsunshine, but cool especially in the
OL,11,Fwind near coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry and mostly sunny
OL,14,Fevening. Lengthy clear spells
OL,15,Fovernight will allow areas of fog and
OL,16,Flow cloud to develop, with frost
OL,17,Fpossible especially in prone rural
OL,18,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
