OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F170A1776917029
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA chilly start once again,
OL,6,Fwith early frost, fog and low cloud
OL,7,Fsoon clearing to leave another dry and
OL,8,Fsunny day. Remaining cooler near
OL,9,Fcoasts, although coastal winds easing
OL,10,Fsomewhat.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,13,Fdry during this period, with sunny
OL,14,Fspells likely. Risk of overnight fog
OL,15,Fand frost. Often cool near coasts, but
OL,16,Fwarm inland. Breezy along coasts on
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
